Method Detail

apply

T apply(Substitution s)
Applies the specified substitution to the Replaceable object.

If the specified substitution does not apply to the object, then returns the object unchanged. If the result of applying the substitution in this object has an invalid state, this method should throw an IllegalArgumentException.

Parameters:
s - The substitution to apply
Returns:
The object that results from the application of the specified substitution
